mixin service-kambali-bekas
  dl.services
    dt
      b Visit to the Bird Rehabilation Center (Kambali Bekas)
      p.
        The Rehabilation Center is a must see for all bird lovers visiting the area. The center houses wild caught parrots recovered from the illegal pet trade. Birds that can survive in the wild and are deemed healthy are released back to the jungles they came from.
      p 
        |Group size: No limit
        br
        |Duration: 1 hour
    dd.gallery
      +service-picture('kambali-bekas/_Q5A3005.jpg', 'Moluccan Cockatoos waiting to be released')
      +service-picture('kambali-bekas/_Q5A3009.jpg')
      +service-picture('kambali-bekas/_Q5A3015.jpg')
